/*------------------------------------------------------------------
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (QuickNote) (Ver. 0.4.0)

Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.0.5 - Last Update: 22.12.2008
--------------------------------------------------------------------
***IMPORTANT: to make this style work properly, you also NEED the
default "Nav-Style Sidebar Vista" style and "All-In-One Sidebar"
extension installed. And obviously the "QUICKNOTE" EXTENSION.***
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
 1. Integrates with "Nav-Style Sidebar Vista" style.
 2. Gives the Nav-Style to the "QuickNote" Sidebar Extension.
 3. Skins almost everything.
 4. Supports "All-in-One Sidebar" extension.
 5. Redesigns the QuickNote interface for looking better.
 6. Highly Customizable.
 7. Integrates with the other "Nav-Style" styles.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Notes:
-This style skins the "QuickNote" Panel ONLY, but it can integrate
 with other "Nav-Style Sidebar" styles for more extensions support
 (read below).

-Works better with AIOS installed (as it was meant to be).
 
-Do not use other styles that changes the Sidebar/Quicknote
 settings.

-QuickNote Extension is a little bugged, the icon doesn't have a
 selected state so it won't change the background color (at least
 until they fix this bug).
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Downloads-panel:
 If you have AIOS installed and want to use the Downloads-Panel in
 the Sidebar, you need the "Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (Downloads)"
 style.

Addons-panel:
 If you have AIOS installed and want to use the Addons-Panel in
 the Sidebar, you need the "Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (Addons)"
 style.

More Extensions-panels:
 If you want more sidebar Extensions skinned, you also need the
 "Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (EXT. NAME)" style that supports the
 Extension panel you want to skin.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMIZING:

 1. QUICKNOTE TOOLBARS BG COLOR.
 2. NAV-STYLE ITEMS OPACITY.
 3. TAB-1 TEXT/BACKGROUND SETTINGS.
 4. TAB-2 TEXT/BACKGROUND SETTINGS.
 5. TAB-3 TEXT/BACKGROUND SETTINGS.
 6. TAB-4 TEXT/BACKGROUND SETTINGS.

> GO TO BOTTOM OF THE PAGE TO CUSTOMIZE
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Supported Extensions:
 QuickNote, All-in-One Sidebar (AIOS).

Integrates with:
 MBlue Combine Nav-Buttons Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Url-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Buttons Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Tabs Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Statusbar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Throbber Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Bookmarks-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Awesome-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Menubar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Popup Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista
>MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (QuickNote)
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (Addons, Downloads, Extensions)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Updates:
 22.12.2008 Ver. 0.4.0 = added namespace
 16.09.2008 Ver. 0.3.0 = ready to release
 13.09.2008 Ver. 0.2.5 = added more info
 11.09.2008 Ver. 0.2.2 = better integration
